                      <br>
                      <p>Name your camera group.</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- /margin -->

                    <div class="margin">
                      <p>Now open the <strong>Add Device</strong> dialogue to add your camera. You need to type in your cameras UID (Point-2-Point User Identification) which can be found in the cameras web user interfaces under network / p2p. Please also read the documentation on P2P from the download area linked above. Please make sure to use the password for the <strong>admin account</strong> of your camera! Name the camera and assign it to the group generated earlier.</p>
                      <br>
                        <amp-img
                            on="tap:lightbox5"
